title: They've got Ant and Dec excited... See the first teasers for this year's I'm A Celeb - I'm A Celebrity Reality TV
text: Reality TV lovers had extra reason to get excited tonight, as ITV aired its first teasers for this year's I'm A Celebrity... Get Me Out Of Here! during The X Factor.Presenters Ant and Dec were certainly delighted to welcome the show's return, tweeting: "Is that jungle drums I hear in the ad break of #XFactor!? That's exciting innit!? D #ImACeleb."I'm a Celebrity... Get Me Out of Here! 2015 rumours: Who's entering the jungle?The presenting duo also later tweeted a link to another of the teasers, which shows the treetops of the jungle while Ant and Dec are heard screaming for help in the distance.But if viewers think this is a hint that the duo will be taking part in this year's show as contestants, they're sadly mistaken.The pair tweeted a response to a fan who commented that the pair should enter the jungle which seemed to totally rule it out, writing: "Absolutely NO chance. Zero. Zip. Nada. None. Nope. Stop it. I'll smash your face in.... D #ImACeleb."We'll take that as a no then....
